        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>pak choi</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the<strong> pak choi </strong>in half, separating the <strong>white base </strong>and <strong>green tops</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>white base </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1670925482748-x200.jpg",
