            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fable mushrooms are charred, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670925488095-x200.jpg",
