            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and<strong> rice vinegar</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>star anise</strong>, 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>and a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
