            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pak choi </strong>and<strong> whole leaves</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until the pak choi is tender and the sauce has thickened – this is your<strong> Chinese-style fable mushroom braise</strong></p>",
